yingyinNormal.zh: 他们不可能废除法律，你必须发表声明才能被释放。

yingyinNormal.en: To have a desire build up within you and be denied any opportunity for release.
yingyinNormal.zh: 心中逐渐建立起了强烈的欲望，最后却只能憋着，无处释放。

yingyinNormal.en: Last night, I was feeling in need of sexual release when I happened to come across your mother.
yingyinNormal.zh: 昨晚我有释放性需求的感觉时，恰好想到你的母亲。

yingyinNormal.en: Can't imagine why that would be. Maybe it has something to do with Elizabeth being up for release?
yingyinNormal.zh: 真不知道为什么呢。也许和伊丽莎白即将被释放有关。

yingyinNormal.en: He was being treated well and was grateful to President Petrov for granting his imminent release.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他一直得到善待，并感谢佩特罗夫总统即将批准释放他。

yingyinNormal.en: Is he on now? You release the Millers, then we put him on. No, you don't get to dictate terms.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他在线吗？你释放米勒一家，我们就让他跟你通话。不，你无权谈条件。

yingyinNormal.en: They're finding that when plants are attacked, they also release an unseen gas from their leaves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 它们发现当植物被攻击时，它们会从叶子中释放一种无色无味的气体。

yingyinNormal.en: Once you bring in your verdict, let me know and justice will be done. Justice? What will you do with them? Early release.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等你作出判决，通知我一声。正义会得到伸张。正义？你要对他们做什么？提前释放。

yingyinNormal.en: You will release the daughter and the mother or you will never hear from me again, and you will lose your chance to speak to your leader. Tell me now.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你得释放女儿和母亲，否则我再也不会与你联络了，而且你会失去与你领袖通话的机会，马上说。

yingyinNormal.en: Here's my question. I successfully negotiated the release of Caroline and Melissa Miller. Then you stepped in. You didn't let me finish the job. Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想问你，我成功的谈判让卡洛琳和梅莉莎·米勒得以释放但你插手进你没让我完成任务，为什么？

yingyinNormal.en: Wait. When Peter was state's attorney, he offered Sweeney a deal early release in return for wearing a wire. That's an ethics violation.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等下，彼得做州检察官那会儿他和斯威尼谈了笔交易，以安装窃听器为条件换取提前释放，这是个道德问题。

yingyinNormal.en: These same cells are triggered to release enormous amounts of serotonin, along with other neurotransmitters like dopamine and norepinephrine, which trigger even more electrochemical firing in the brain.
yingyinNormal.zh: 释放出大量的复合胺，还有其他的神经传递介质，例如多巴胺跟正肾上腺素这更引起了脑中更大的化学反应。

yingyinNormal.en: Either charge me or release me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要么起诉我，要么放了我。

yingyinNormal.en: Already delivered to Congress, we put out a release.
yingyinNormal.zh: 已经送到国会并通知媒体了。

yingyinNormal.en: Start checklist complete. You really think they'll release us?
yingyinNormal.zh: 起飞检查单确认完毕，你真认为他们会放行？

yingyinNormal.en: Release the baby!
yingyinNormal.zh: 放小孩!

yingyinNormal.en: Maya, release the Farkle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛雅，放开法尔科。

examination_example.sentence: India <highlight>released</highlight> its AI ethics strategy this spring.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 今年春天，印度发布了人工智能伦理战略。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Release</highlight> a lifted GDP growth forecast
examination_example.sentence_trans: 发布上调的GDP增长预测

examination_example.sentence: Quicker turnarounds mean less wasted inventory, more frequent <highlight>releases</highlight>, and more profit.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 更快的周转意味着更少的库存浪费，更频繁的新品发布和更多的利润。

sense_info_list.en: to let sb/sth come out of a place where they have been kept or trapped

examination_example.sentence: Next, the researchers trapped the robots in cages and gave the rats the opportunity to <highlight>release</highlight> them by pressing a lever.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 接下来，研究人员将机器人困在笼子里，并给老鼠按压杠杆的机会来释放它们。

examination_example.sentence: Oxytocin is made primarily in the central lower part of the brain, and some of it is <highlight>released</highlight> into the bloodstream.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 催产素最初在大脑中心偏下部位产生，部分被释放到血液中。

examination_example.sentence: Soon after his father's <highlight>release</highlight> from prison, Dickens got a better job as errand boy in law offices.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 父亲出狱后不久，狄更斯找到了一份更好的工作，在律师事务所当跑腿的。
